title: The Ultimate Guide to Android Tablets - 2014  UK
description:
The Ultimate Guide to Android Tablets - 2014  UK

116 Pages | HQ PDF | English | 20 MB 


The Ultimate Guide to Android Tablets illustrates with clear screenshots and step-by-step walkthroughs to help you get the most out of your tablet. With tips, in-depth guides and reviews to help you discover the world of Android tablets, we show you how to set up your tablet from scratch, introduce key features and learn about Google's latest tablet software: Android 4.3, also known as Jelly Bean. Whether you're thinking of buying, have already bought an Android tablet or are simply curious to know more, this is the guide for you.
